NG0234:1: gnas shing dgod pa 'di lta ste //
NG0234:2: gru gsum gang 'dod snying po ming *//
NG0234:3: zla gam gsum la stong pa'i ming *//
NG0234:4: rgya gram rtsa ba'i 'bru bzhi dgod //
NG0234:5: mu khyud rbod gtong gdug pa'i ming *//
NG0234:6: bcu gnyis rtsibs la spu gri sbyar /
NG0234:7: kha sbyar dar dang sngon dmar bsdam //
NG0234:8: dur ma gru gsum ling+ga mnag / phyag rgya zil gnon gsal byas la //
NG0234:9: zhag lnga bskul zhing mchog phur gdab //
NG0234:10: nad pa bdug la phying pas dgab //
NG0234:11: thon nas bka' rten gnyan sar mnan //
NG0234:12: gnod pa kun gyi sbyor ba gcod //
NG0234:13: drag sngags sbyor ba las tshogs brgyad //
NG0234:14: sarba tsit+ta ro myags kha tham /
NG0234:15: 'drid phyung shag rbad srog la breng shag dun /
NG0234:16: dun e ram hur thum dzahdzah sa na ga snying gzer sbur nan /
NG0234:17: kham shag rtsa la rbad sa na ga dzah sa na ga thum /
NG0234:19: sa na ga tsit+ta ro myags kha thums /
NG0234:24: 'drid yam bzlog sbur nan trig nan /
NG0234:28: sarba sha trum stam+b+ha ya na sha ya nan phat /
NG0234:29: las rnams rgyas pa'i rim pa ni //
NG0234:30: che ba dril ba'i las tshogs 'di //
NG0234:31: thun mong spyod pa'i las su bshad //
NG0234:32: srog dmar len spu gri'i rgyud las thun mong gi las bshad pa'i le'u ste bzhi pa'o //  //
NG0234:33: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis khyad par gyi sbyor ba'i las 'di gsungs so //
NG0234:34: brda' don thabs kyis dgrol ba'i las //
NG0234:35: ba dang 'o ma zho dang mar //
NG0234:36: zhun mar snum gyi snying po bcud //
NG0234:37: snying po la sogs bzhi gnyis ldan //
NG0234:38: yengs med bstan pa bgrod pa'i stobs //
NG0234:39: dmar len sngags kyi snying phyung yin //
NG0234:40: gong mthun rgyu las 'khor lo bca' //
NG0234:41: dpa' brtul drag po'i stobs kyis spyad //
NG0234:42: gdug byed phag mo'i lto ba ru //
NG0234:43: srid pa'i khyams khang srog sdud bca' /
NG0234:44: khyams khang lto na brnag pa'i gzugs //
NG0234:45: spyi gtsug snying gar mtshon cha bca' //
NG0234:46: mu khyud bzhi dbus ming rus bri //
NG0234:47: phyi rim rgya gram rtsa ba'i sngags //
NG0234:48: yang logs bcu gnyis spu gri mtshon //
NG0234:49: mu khyud ming rus lto sbyar bsad //
NG0234:50: rus sbal lto na mtshon cha'i rtsibs //
NG0234:51: rtse mo nang bstan spu gri bzlog / phag mo'i lus la mnan pa'i sngags //
NG0234:52: 'bru bzhi srog dang a mu ka / bskyod pa'i yan lag dbugs la zhon //
NG0234:53: don gnyis bsdus la sbyor ba bya /
NG0234:54: kha sbyor dur ma brnag pa'i gzugs //
NG0234:55: rgyu rkyen drug cus byas kyang tsog pur bzhag / snying gar mchog phur ya mas gdab //
NG0234:56: bsgom bskul drag sngags bsnol mar brdeg / rab kyi rkang thon bsnol mar gcod //
NG0234:57: 'bring gi bcu bar bsnol mar brdeg / dman pas brgya bar bsnol mar gcod //
NG0234:58: dug lnga sku lnga ye shes lnga //
NG0234:59: gsang lam sgo dgu rtsa lam 'asngug / bde ba'i ye shes rang la gsal //
NG0234:62: dmar nag rtog pa'i khrag dkyil nas //
NG0234:63: bsdu ba'i yi ge gsum gyis 'phrog / tsa na'i 'bras bus rten la thim //
NG0234:64: thod par snying po bcud sdud bya //
NG0234:65: klu la bcud par 'gran zlar gtad //
NG0234:66: gzhan du bcud dang spu gri sbyar //
NG0234:67: yi ge byin can steng du brtag btab kyang *//
NG0234:68: phyag rgya chos sku sprul bsam yas //
NG0234:69: thob cing bgrod pa sngags kyi stobs //
NG0234:70: de nas bcom ldan 'das nyid kyi //
NG0234:71: sku gsung thugs rdo rje las /
NG0234:72: mchog gi drag sngags 'di bton to //
NG0234:73: srog la rtsa khrag snying thums ril nan ri shag rbad /
NG0234:75: bsad pa'i sbyor ba drag po'i las //
NG0234:76: nye bar gcig dril bsdeb pa'o //
NG0234:77: gzhan yang gab sbas brnag pa'i las //
NG0234:78: rgyal blon stobs can yul srung la //
NG0234:79: rten gyi gzugs brnyan rgya shog la //
NG0234:80: phag mo dang ni sdig pa'i lto ba ru //
NG0234:81: mu khyud rim pa bzhi bzhir bskor //
NG0234:82: dbus su ling+ga lus la bca' //
NG0234:83: nr-i dang rgya gram rtsibs bcu drug / rtsa ba spu gri ming rus khams //
NG0234:84: 'chas la ling+ga'i steng du brnag / nyin zhag phrugs
NG0234:85: gcig gsum du brnag / mtshon cha'i brdeg thabs snga
NG0234:86: ma bzhin // rngam tshig lus bskyod lu mar gtad //
NG0234:87: drag sngags sbyor ba 'di lta ste //
NG0234:88: dgra bo'i srog la hur long rbad //
NG0234:89: nr-i rtsa khrag thibs hur thums dza //
NG0234:90: ming dang gzugs kyis rims dal 'bebs //
NG0234:91: rgyal ba'i ye shes brnag rnam mang yang par bshad //
NG0234:92: gzhan yang mdze rims dbab pa'i las //
NG0234:93: sbal pa'i lto bar brnag pa'i gzugs //
NG0234:94: snying gar nr-i dza ya ma ra ya rbad //
NG0234:95: bkod la mdze can khrag gis bsku //
NG0234:96: dkar nag gdug pa lto sbyar la //
NG0234:97: sdig pa phag mo'i lto ba ru //
NG0234:98: mu khyud bzhi bzhi rgya gram rtsibs //
NG0234:99: gong bzhin bkod la kha sbyar bca' //
NG0234:100: klu nag sdig pa'i snying gar gtad //
NG0234:101: drag sngags 'bum tsho dgu ru sbyar //
NG0234:102: de yis mdze rims yams su 'babs //
NG0234:103: thod pa mdze can dmar chod la //
NG0234:104: spos chen gu gul bdud rtsis bsang *//
NG0234:105: drag sngags sbyor ba gnyis su bsdeb //
NG0234:106: e ga tsa thun khrag yam rngubs shig srog la bam ril ram shag rbad /
NG0234:107: dza na ga dzi la bam hur thums dza /
NG0234:108: nr-i dz+wa la dzi bam tsit+ta khas /
NG0234:110: dz+wa la 'bar ba'i las su bshad //
NG0234:111: gzhan yang lo tog 'joms pa'i las //
NG0234:112: nye bar spogs med gcig tu dril //
NG0234:113: sde brgyad kun gyi mthu bsdus nas //
NG0234:114: thod pa gsum la ming gzugs yul //
NG0234:115: sbyor ba bsdus la gta' ma gzhug khrag dang phur pa mon thod du //
NG0234:116: sngags bstim 'bum rdzogs dbab pa brtsam //
NG0234:117: dug khrag bya phag gsur chen brun //
NG0234:118: du bas gzugs gzir lcags phur gdab //
NG0234:119: rang nyid phyag rgya zil gnon bsgom //
NG0234:120: drag sngags sbyor ba dril la brdeg / e ka ya rngubs shag mugs ru myags /
NG0234:122: hri na ga snying gzer sbur yam thun ya shag hril b+h+yo /
NG0234:123: khyad par gdug pa'i rten la @#//
NG0234:125: lha btsan bstan la the brang gzir //
NG0234:127: srog dmar len gyi rgyud las /
NG0234:128: khyad par gyi le'u ste lnga pa'o ///
NG0234:129: de nas ma mo'i tshogs 'bum sdes /
NG0234:130: // / de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis snying po mchog nye bar dril ba 'di gsungs so //
NG0234:131: 'jig rten dregs pa'i mthu bsdus nas //
NG0234:132: nag po bde ba'i 'bru la dril //
NG0234:133: rno dbal mtshon cha'i rgyal por bca' //
NG0234:134: sngags kyi lus la spu gri gdags //
NG0234:136: sngags pa bon po rigs med la //
NG0234:137: rang bdud phyag cha rang bdud 'bebs //
NG0234:138: de yi sbyor ba rgyas pa ni //
NG0234:139: chos sku bde ba'i rang bzhin las //
NG0234:140: bde ba'i ye shes rang shar ba //
NG0234:141: bde ba'i thig le mnyam par rdzogs //
NG0234:144: dge bcu ma yengs mtshan brjod pa //
NG0234:145: bdud dang gshed ma rlung las bslang *//
NG0234:146: gzugs brnyan 'khor lo ma yin te //
NG0234:147: gang yin snying gi 'khor lo la //
NG0234:148: dwangs ma bzhi la gsang gshed bzhi //
NG0234:149: rtsa phran brgyad la phyi nang gshed //
NG0234:150: mdud pa bzhi la mtshon cha'i dbal //
NG0234:151: rtsa phran yang logs 'chi bdag bdud //
NG0234:152: rtsa sgo gzhan tshogs b+h+yo rbad nan //
NG0234:153: 'dus pa gsum la yab yum e //
NG0234:154: dkar nag chags pa rten gzhi'i 'bru //
NG0234:155: bskul bas rang rgyud gshed du ldang *//
NG0234:156: ma yi khong nas rnam shes 'phrog / 'bru gsum lcags sder 'dzings pa'i tshul //
NG0234:157: rtsa dang srog bcad lus srog dbye //
NG0234:158: tsit+ta'i dkyil nas 'bru gcig sdud kyang 'phrog cing sdud //
NG0234:159: de yis rang gshed rang la 'bebs //
NG0234:160: de bzhin lus kyi 'khor lo la //
NG0234:161: phung po lnga la srog bdud gshed //
NG0234:162: gtso bo gsang ba'i gshed bzhi ldang *//
NG0234:163: rnam shes tshogs brgyad phyi nang gshed //
NG0234:164: yul brgyad de bzhin gshed mo brgyad //
NG0234:165: bzlas pa'i rkyen gyi rgyud las ldang *//
NG0234:166: skye mched bcu gnyis 'chi bdag bdud /
NG0234:167: khams chen bco brgyad sgrol ging bdud //
NG0234:168: yan lag bzhi la bla rkun bzhi //
NG0234:169: so dang sgal tshigs sha za'i tshogs //
NG0234:170: bzlas pa'i rta bskyod yi ge bskul //
NG0234:171: rang gi bdud po rang la dbab //
NG0234:172: gshed rgyud phyi yi bdud du dbab //
NG0234:173: b+h+yo bzhi gnad kyis gang bsgrub pa'i //
NG0234:175: phyi rgyud bdud kyi 'khor lo bshad //
NG0234:176: de bzhin gzugs brnyan 'khor lo yang *//
NG0234:177: zhe sdang sdig pa'i lto ba dang *//
NG0234:178: phrag dog bse yi sbal pa la //
NG0234:179: ltor bar sngags pa'i gzugs bris la //
NG0234:180: snying gar mu khyud bzhi ru bskor //
NG0234:181: rgya gram bzhi dang rtsibs bcu drug / mtshon cha phyi nang brtse sprad la //
NG0234:182: ming rus snying po rten la brdeg / gshin rje la sogs gang 'grub pa'i //
NG0234:183: rnam shes 'bru re dbus su 'pho phob kyang *//
NG0234:184: mchod rten nag po'i 'og tu gnan //
NG0234:185: las 'di gu h+ya a ti rgya //
NG0234:187: nyid kyi sku gsung thugs rdo rje las rang gshed skul ba'i drag sngags 'di bton to //
NG0234:191: nr-i srog la hur thums dza /
NG0234:192: bod pa dngos a mu ka / rnam shes 'bru re dbus su dgod //
NG0234:193: bdud dang gshed po rang las ldang *//
NG0234:194: ho phan srog 'dzin las su bshad //
NG0234:195: srog dmar len spu gri'i rgyud las rang gshed rang
NG0234:196: la 'bebs pa'i le'u ste drug pa'o //[ 。]// de
NG0234:197: nas bcom ldan 'das kyis srin mo lcags thag mgo
NG0234:198: dgu ma'i sbyor ba 'di gsungs so //
NG0234:199: rgyal ba'i bka' las 'das pa dang *//
NG0234:200: mtshams med lnga la spyod pa dang *//
NG0234:201: dgon pa'i gnas su phra ma dang *//
NG0234:202: dam chos dge bcu smod pa dang *//
NG0234:203: bden pa'i don la log lta spyod //
NG0234:204: de tshe sngags kyi dmod pa bor //
NG0234:205: rten gsum sngags kyi 'khor lo bca' //
NG0234:207: rgya shog dar ram ro ras la //
NG0234:208: phag mo sdig pa'i lto ba ru //
NG0234:209: thig bzhi brnag pa'i snying gar bskor //
NG0234:210: gru gsum rgya gram rtse mo dgu //
NG0234:211: de bzhin nang du rtse bstan dgu //
NG0234:212: rgya gram e grangs rtsa ba brgyad //
NG0234:213: mtshon cha'i rtse la spu gri'i so //
NG0234:214: phyi nang mtshon cha bsnol mar dgod //
NG0234:215: dbus dang mtshams su brnag pa'i gzugs ming yang */
NG0234:216: kha sbyor tshon skud dong rtsar brnag / rang nyid che ba'i nga rgyal nas //
NG0234:217: mdun na lcags thag mgo dgu+u ma //
NG0234:218: dbu dgu steng ma bya yi dbu //
NG0234:219: dur bya khra dang bzhad kyi dbu //
NG0234:220: nang khrol glo snying za zhing rngam //
NG0234:221: bar gyi dbu gsum dud 'gro'i dbu //
NG0234:222: dom dang dred dang chu srin dbu //
NG0234:223: rtsa gcad khrag dang nang khrol za //
NG0234:224: rtsa ba'i dbu gsum khro mo'i dbu //
NG0234:225: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing la //
NG0234:226: mche ba zang yag mi ro za //
NG0234:227: spyan nas khrag 'dzag dug rlangs shangs //
NG0234:228: sku stod zhing lpags thod pa sbrul //
NG0234:229: sku smad re lde dril bu khrag / g.yas dgu mngon bsgral snying khrag 'dzin //
NG0234:230: g.yon pa dgu na thod zor bskyod //
NG0234:231: stag dang spyang ki ba glang mon //
NG0234:232: dred mo snel ma khyi dang phag / 'thom nag g.yas pa dug khrag zor //
NG0234:233: zhabs brgyad dregs pa'i snying gar brdzis //
NG0234:235: skra dang kha spu me ru 'bar //
NG0234:236: de la bka' bsgo bskul zhing mngag / dgu bskor thun gyis mngags pa yi //
NG0234:237: las grub mtha' ru gzir la mnan //
NG0234:238: brag dmar srin mo'i sgrom du gtad //
NG0234:239: dus bzhi las kyi kha gso bya //
NG0234:240: de nas bcom ldan 'das nyid kyi sku gsung thugs
NG0234:241: rdo rje las rno myur spu gri'i drag sngags 'di
NG0234:242: bton to // e bam ram khram shig tsit+ta rngubs /
NG0234:243: dgra bo'i srog la thun rmugs ling shag rbad /
NG0234:244: stobs can thams cad nye bar 'joms //
NG0234:245: rno myur las kyi brnag par bshad //
NG0234:246: gzhan yang lo tog gzhom pa'i las //
NG0234:247: dme thod nang du me long bsar //
NG0234:248: gser dngul zangs lcags rdo nag @#//
NG0234:249: bzhag / ra dmar nal bu khyi nag snying *//
NG0234:250: steng du gling bzhi rtsibs brgyad dgab //
NG0234:251: de steng srin mo mgo dgu'i sku //
NG0234:252: mthing nag dar gyis bkab la bzlas /
NG0234:253: khrag sna gsum dang dug bsres la //
NG0234:254: ling+ga ming byang g.yag ru gzhug / smyug ma tshigs gsum smin pa la //
NG0234:255: ltas ngan sgro yis bsgron la bzhag / zhag lnga'i bar du drag sngags bzlas //
NG0234:256: gser mde'u zhu zhing 'phan chad na //
NG0234:257: mda' bcas blug la dgra la brdeg / srin mo drag tu bskul la 'phang *//
NG0234:258: drag sngags sbyor ba brtul zhugs bstud la yang bstims //
NG0234:259: e bam ram khram shig tsit+ta rngubs /
NG0234:261: lam ram sma sha hril hur kham sho yengs phrom shar seng khrol b+h+yo /
NG0234:262: gnam thog chen po dbab pa'i las //
NG0234:263: nye bar gyur pa'i sbyor ba bshad //
NG0234:264: gzhan yang srin mo g.yel ba na //
NG0234:265: grog mkhar rgya tshil sa dmar la //
NG0234:266: bong bu'i bdud rtsis legs sprus la //
NG0234:267: srin mo mgo dgu'i gzugs brnyan bca' //
NG0234:268: snying gar gru gsum snying po gzhug / drag sngags bzlog la stobs kyis gzir //
NG0234:269: srin mo bos la khrag gis bran //
NG0234:270: phur pas bsdigs la dbang du bsdus //
NG0234:271: srin mo bka' nan zhabs 'og gzhug / gzir ba'i sngags 'dis khri ru brab //
NG0234:272: phur pa 'dril la be con brdung *//
NG0234:273: e ka ya ma bam ram khram shig tsit+ta rngubs /
NG0234:274: ya ma rag sha hur thums dza /
NG0234:276: de yis ma mo dbang du bsdus //
NG0234:277: rang dbang med par las la mngag / sngags dang bdud rtsis srin mo gso //
NG0234:278: ling+ga ming rus brnag par gzhug / zhag gsum thun brab ro khung mnan //
NG0234:279: 'byung ba dkrugs la gnam sa sbyar //
NG0234:280: drag sngags brgya bar thun du brang *//
NG0234:281: lus srog tsit+ta'i sgo phye nas //
NG0234:282: lha dang rang sngags bdud du 'bebs //
NG0234:283: sha lpags go cha bral nas bshig / rtsa dang srog zungs bcad nas skems //
NG0234:284: tshe srog dwangs snyigs phye nas sdud //
NG0234:285: brnag pa'i las kyi mtha' ru phyin //
NG0234:286: drag sngags sbyor ba bskul la brdeg / e khram bam rngubs ram ta tsit+ta khram /
NG0234:287: dgra bo'i srog la ma ra rbad /
NG0234:289: kun gyi mtha' ru 'di sbyar na //
NG0234:290: brnag pa'i lus srog 'byed pa yin //
NG0234:291: srog dmar len spu gri'i rgyud las srin mo shel gyi dmod pa'i le'u ste bdun pa'o ///
NG0234:292: / de nas yang bcom ldan 'das kyis srung ba
NG0234:293: thams cad kyi mchog tu dril ba 'di gsungs so
NG0234:294: // thabs ldan bde ba'i snying po mchog / byin rlabs kun 'dus drag po'i brda //
NG0234:295: lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang nyid las //
NG0234:296: zil gnon phyag rgya sngags kyi mchog / snying po srog dang brda mi sbyar //
NG0234:297: tsit+ta'i dkyil nas 'bru gcig 'phrog / dug rlangs zhen pa'i stobs dang dbyung *//
NG0234:298: las dang sbyor ba nus pa gcod //
NG0234:299: spyi dang sgos srog rang gnad 'phrog / rten gyi mtshon cha gnas su dbab //
NG0234:300: phag mo sdig pa'i lto ba ru //
NG0234:303: nyi shu gnyis rtsibs gdug par ldan //
NG0234:304: gru gsum gang gnod gzugs dang ming *//
NG0234:305: rgya gram de bzhin rtsa ba'i sngags //
NG0234:306: mtshams dang gsang mdzod re'u mig / nyi shu gnyis la spu gri'i so //
NG0234:307: lto sbyar phag thod dug khrag brnag / zhag gsum sngags bzlas bsreg la mnan //
NG0234:308: gang 'dod ming dang snying po bsdeb //
NG0234:309: gzir dang dug dbyung srog 'phrog gcod //
NG0234:310: spyi srog sgos srog 'bru gsum dbrog / 'bru gsum mtha' ru sbyor ba gcod //
NG0234:311: 'di med las sogs yug pa brkyang *//
NG0234:312: 'di de bde dang smin pa'i mchog / de nas
NG0234:313: bcom ldan 'das nyid kyi sku gsung thugs rdo rje
NG0234:314: las srung ba'i mchog tu dril ba'i drag sngags 'di
NG0234:315: bton to // e myags ya rngubs mug shag ka dun /
NG0234:317: ha la ha la tsa ma ri phyung */
NG0234:323: ma ma ru lu ru lu ma /
NG0234:339: dza ya dzah ra ti ra /
NG0234:342: rtsa ba spu gri rno dbal mtshon //
NG0234:343: bgrod pa'i phyag rgya stobs med na //
NG0234:345: stobs ldan bgrod pa'i gdeng ldan na //
NG0234:346: rno myur sbyor ba kun 'joms yin //
NG0234:347: rtsa ba bcu gnyis dmar len mtshon //
NG0234:348: las kyi mchong chen rang bstan shis //
NG0234:349: mtha' ru bdug bran bum pas sbyang *//
NG0234:350: phyi nang nad bkrus ye shes chus //
NG0234:351: phyag rgya gcig pas nus pa bskyed //
NG0234:352: drag po'i rang bzhin btsan thabs gzir //
NG0234:354: 'di ni srung ba kun gyi mchog / rgyal ba'i thig le 'dus par bshad //
NG0234:355: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis sbyor ba'i mchog tu gsang ba 'di gsungs so //
NG0234:356: sme gsum tsha chus rgyu byugs la //
NG0234:357: gdug pa'i me la bdug la bca' //
NG0234:358: dug dang bse yi sdig sbal gnyis //
NG0234:359: lte bar brnag pa'i dbang po dgod //
NG0234:360: snying gar mu khyud bzhis bskor la //
NG0234:361: gru gsum zla gam rgya gram rtsibs //
NG0234:362: gdug pa'i ra bas de bzhin gdams //
NG0234:363: gri skud mdze yams mche ba'i mtshon //
NG0234:364: rgya gram gab sbas rtsa ba'i sngags //
NG0234:365: drug gnyis nang ldan gsod pa'i mtshon //
NG0234:366: zhe sdang bzhi stor mnan gzir brgyad //
NG0234:367: dbus dang ra 'ug ming rus khams //
NG0234:368: zla kham lha dang srung ba'i ming *//
NG0234:369: rtsibs mchan mtshon cha gnod pa'i ming *//
NG0234:370: dug khrag tsha ba'i stobs bskus la /
NG0234:371: kha sbyar thod chen rgya gram e //
